<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Reinprecht II. von Walsee, Hauptmann ob der Enns</head><p>Der Rat bittet um Unterstützung und Geleit für die Nürnberger Gesandtschaft auf dem Weg zu König Sigismund.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_409" id="204r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l13">Dem Edeln herren / <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Reinprehten von vvalſee </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l14">Hauptman Ob der Enns </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l16">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als 
<add><ab facs="#facs_409_r1l15">vvir </ab></add> vnſer erber botſchaft <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l17"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> Römiſchen künig etc ſchicken / Biten vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l18"><expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleıſʒ / daʒ Jr ew <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> botſchaft durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l19"><expan>günſtiklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſſet <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein / vnd beſunder ſie mit ſıcherm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l20">geleite durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> herſchaft vnd gepiete 
<del rend="strikethrough">fürſehen auff </del> ab vnd auff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_409_r1l21">fürſehen wöllet / Als etc / das wöllen etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>valentı<ex>ni</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_409" id="204r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dem edeln herren, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Reinprehten von Walsee,
                        hauptman ob der Enns</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als <add>wir</add> unser erber
                        botschaft <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> römischen künig
                        etc., schicken, biten wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edel mit
                                <expan>alle<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, daz ir ew
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan> botschaft durch
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>günstiklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lasset
                            <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein und besunder sie mit sicherm
                        geleite durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> herschaft und gepiete ab und auff
                        fürsehen wöllet. Als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Valenti<ex>ni</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
